  <p><b>Handmade Fused Glass Coasters</b><br>
Each set of coasters comes wrapped in a ribbon - perfect for a gift. These make quite a statement in a room, whether on the coffee table or in the kitchen, bedroom or boardroom. Each coaster is approximately 10cm x 10cm in size and no two are ever the same. Due to popular demand most of my makes are commissions these days, so if there are no coasters for general sale I would love to create one or more especially for you. Prices from &pound;7.50. For ideas pop over to my <a href="gallery.php" onclick="return changeLoc('gallery', 'category', '2')">'Glasspirations Gallery'</a> page to see the coasters I have previously designed.<br>
<span style="font-size:18px; color:blue">(<i>Click on picture for more details</i>)</span></p>
